{"type": "article", "id": 3428, "title": "Joseph Joseph存储套装", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-11T07:27:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232801Bokzibf16rId9wZq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国厨具品牌 Joseph Joseph 有一款名为「Nest™ Storage」的存储套装，将不同大小的存储容器与盖子巧妙地融合在一个空间内。如今市面上大多数食品储存容器地问题在于，即便不需要使用时，它们也需要分别存储，占据很大的厨房空间。而这款「Nest™ Storage」真正做到了节省空间，不同大小的容器，盖子被分为不同的颜色，容易可以按照大小堆叠放入一个空间，盖子也可以堆叠一一对应扣在上访，保证了内部空间的密不透风。提供 2 个、4 个以及 6 个三种套装，定价 9－40 英镑不等，<a href=\"http://www.josephjoseph.com/product/nest-storage\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232759vdBzUn6TkOpjIiwA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232759XDJlvWoxtAZK0Ccu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232800xFvpwHzMCGDnTWjm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232800h5EJiK4ofvGgYH1P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8890625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232801C9Ko6BqONs1AGml5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}